data.enText: dirt that forms a layer on the surface of sth
a face covered with grime and sweat

tr: the state of being covered with unclean things

example: don't soil your clothes when you play outside!

value.def: Grime is dirt which has collected on the surface of something.

example.ex: Kelly got the grime off his hands before rejoining her in the kitchen.
example.tran: 凯利洗去手上的污垢，又回到厨房来帮她的忙。
